{
  "stem": "2966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had tremendous forests all around us where the Germans didn't dare to go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But our wonderful Ukrainians that lived all around in the villages, they spotted them, and they used to uncover them, and they bring them out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And especially bad it was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In the winter, when the snow was high and these people had to come out to get some food and water, they used to see the-- the footprints in the snow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But yet, some of these people survived in the forest, through the whole-- some of them up to two years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They dug big trenches, they covered it up, and somehow they survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But we had nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I didn't know anybody in those places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They didn't want to take any more people, because food was-- great shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "That was the main problem, was food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And-- and I was still on and off hidden in that place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Then one day, in broad daylight, I had a last pair of pants to sell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So I was wearing two pair of pants on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I was walking the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And to tell you the truth, I did not look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "The Jew was considered with black hair, with a big nose, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I wore no armband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I walked through the streets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like he came from under earth, an SS man, with a gun in my face.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And he says, [GERMAN] hands up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he slapped my face, and he took me to that camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At that time, I gave out-- I gave up already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I was resigned already.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
